title: Make elf.File read the program headers
body:
by **Matthew.Horsnell**: 
What steps will reproduce the problem?
1. Use the elf.Open method to prepare the ELF file for reading
2. Iterate over the Progs

What is the expected output?

You would expect multiple progs regions


What do you see instead?

You see zero progs


Which revision are you using?  (hg identify)
90f9c658e53d+ tip

Please provide any additional information below.
Noted that there is a TODO comment in debug/elf/file.go
